Package com.github.qacore.seleniumtestingtoolbox.annotations

Annotations denoting the roles of types or methods in the overall architecture (at a conceptual, rather than implementation, level).

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AjaxElement
    Identifies an Ajax Element.
    Name
    This annotation is used to describe a component.
    Page
    Mark a field as a Page Object that should be automatically created by Selenium Testing Toolbox.
    PageComponent
    Mark a field as a Page Object Component that should be automatically created by Selenium Testing Toolbox.
    PageRepository
    Mark a field as a Page Object Repository that should be automatically created by Selenium Testing Toolbox.
